18
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:39,848
=Episode 15=

19
00:01:48,891 --> 00:01:49,891
How did you escape?

20
00:01:52,171 --> 00:01:53,490
Even sect leaders...

21
00:01:54,410 --> 00:01:55,130
Do you remember

22
00:01:55,891 --> 00:01:58,251
