was trying to kill me before?

23
00:01:59,371 --> 00:02:00,410
Am I that valuable?

24
00:02:00,891 --> 00:02:02,050
Why chase me so relentlessly?

25
00:02:06,531 --> 00:02:07,171
20,000 liang?

26
00:02:07,251 --> 00:02:08,251
Impossible!

27
00:02:08,491 --> 00:02:09,410
Must be 200,000 liang.

28
00:02:10,331 --> 00:02:10,931
Two liang.

29
00:02:14,491 --> 00:02:15,130
Your turn.

30
00:02:16,850 --> 00:02:17,290
Wait!

31
00:02:22,450 --> 00:02:23,251
Think I'm someone

32
00:02:23,331 --> 00:02:24,450
who can be bribed

33
00:02:24,570 --> 00:02:25,730
by one liang?

34
00:02:26,850 --> 00:02:28,410
I offered two!

35
00:02:29,570 --> 00:02:30,570
These two liang

36
00:02:30,850 --> 00:02:32,290
double what you'd get

37
00:02:32,610 --> 00:02:33,211
for this job.

38
00:02:34,051 --> 00:02:34,771
How'd you know?

39
00:02:35,410 --> 00:02:36,091
I don't.

40
00:02:36,371 --> 00:02:37,371
Just guessed.

41
00:02:37,971 --> 00:02:39,531
Your throwing skills are divine,

42
00:02:39,850 --> 00:02:41,331
yet you're poor.

43
00:02:41,730 --> 00:02:44,410
Must be the lowest-ranked assassin.

44
00:02:44,890 --> 00:02:48,091
Assassin ranks go Class A to G.

45
00:02:48,290 --> 00:02:50,091
Class A takes 200 liang.

46
00:02:50,450 --> 00:02:51,971
Class B 100 liang.

47
00:02:52,211 --> 00:02:53,491
C 50 liang.

48
00:02:53,771 --> 00:02:54,890
D 10 liang.

49
00:02:55,730 --> 00:02:56,850
E two liang.

50
00:02:56,931 --> 00:02:57,730
G one liang.

51
00:02:58,290 --> 00:03:00,251
A Class A assassin
took the job at 200 liang.

52
00:03:00,531 --> 00:03:01,610
But when

53
00:03:02,211 --> 00:03:03,971
it gets to you...

54
00:03:08,610 --> 00:03:09,211
So,

55
00:03:09,890 --> 00:03:10,931
they do nothing

56
00:03:11,091 --> 00:03:11,890
yet earn

57
00:03:11,971 --> 00:03:13,371
hundreds liang!

58
00:03:13,610 --> 00:03:14,850
I work so hard

59
00:03:15,010 --> 00:03:16,211
yet earn one liang daily!

60
00:03:17,811 --> 00:03:18,651
Exactly!

61
00:03:19,251 --> 00:03:19,771
The middleman

62
00:03:20,010 --> 00:03:21,690
exploits much.

63
00:03:22,690 --> 00:03:23,570
Spot on!

64
00:03:23,771 --> 00:03:24,771
Then why not

65
00:03:25,130 --> 00:03:27,010
take my two liang?

66
00:03:27,290 --> 00:03:28,651
Take it

67
00:03:28,890 --> 00:03:29,931
and pretend to kill me.

68
00:03:30,170 --> 00:03:30,690
Then

69
00:03:30,971 --> 00:03:32,170
grab midnight snack

70
00:03:32,290 --> 00:03:32,971
and get off work.

71
00:03:33,251 --> 00:03:34,331
Perfect, right?

72
00:03:50,091 --> 00:03:51,331
(Money is not working?)

73
00:04:04,811 --> 00:04:05,251
Go.

74
00:04:06,610 --> 00:04:07,051
Wait.

75
00:04:07,491 --> 00:04:07,690
Why?

76
00:04:07,771 --> 00:04:08,331
Knife.

77
00:04:19,691 --> 00:04:20,891
You're ruthless, bro.

78
00:04:23,850 --> 00:04:25,091
It's okay, you can go.

79
00:04:25,211 --> 00:04:25,850
I'll handle it.

80
00:04:26,370 --> 00:04:26,810
Farewell.

81
00:04:39,810 --> 00:04:41,011
Xue Hexu!

82
00:04:54,850 --> 00:04:55,370
What?

83
00:04:56,290 --> 00:04:58,011
Gu Qianfu lied?

84
00:04:58,930 --> 00:05:00,850
He denied coming to kill you

85
00:05:01,370 --> 00:05:02,410
under Grand Tutor's order?

86
00:05:03,370 --> 00:05:04,451
Gu Qianfu is innocent.

87
00:05:04,971 --> 00:05:06,290
The order passed through many.

88
00:05:06,651 --> 00:05:07,490
And Gu Qianfu

89
00:05:07,930 --> 00:05:09,771
didn't know
it is Grand Tutor Zhou's order.

90
00:05:10,531 --> 00:05:11,810
I wonder

91
00:05:12,170 --> 00:05:13,610
why the Jing'an Bureau hired

92
00:05:14,050 --> 00:05:15,211
assassins twice to kill me,

93
00:05:15,490 --> 00:05:16,610
instead of

94
00:05:16,610 --> 00:05:17,451
using their men?

95
00:05:20,730 --> 00:05:21,691
Young Master's missing

96
00:05:22,451 --> 00:05:24,050
likely connects to Grand Tutor Zhou.

97
00:05:24,651 --> 00:05:25,370
Youshou's missing?

98
00:05:25,810 --> 00:05:26,370
When?

99
00:05:28,050 --> 00:05:28,850
Dawn today,

100
00:05:29,571 --> 00:05:30,331
when you departed.

101
00:05:31,011 --> 00:05:32,170
(According to Grand Tutor,)

102
00:05:32,571 --> 00:05:33,971
(Youshou isn't the Crown Prince.)

103
00:05:34,810 --> 00:05:36,531
(What's his relationship
to Grand Tutor?)

104
00:05:37,810 --> 00:05:38,891
(Who am I really?)

105
00:05:40,050 --> 00:05:41,810
The Emperor saw Youshou's portrait.

106
00:05:42,651 --> 00:05:44,131
I'd never surrender him,

107
00:05:44,571 --> 00:05:45,730
nor let you take his place.

108
00:05:49,011 --> 00:05:50,170
Since I take his place,

109
00:05:50,410 --> 00:05:51,571
let's fake my death

110
00:05:51,771 --> 00:05:53,370
to end this hunt!

111
00:05:54,451 --> 00:05:56,850
Youshou has lived
as a shadow for decades

112
00:05:57,290 --> 00:05:58,211
and suffered much.

113
00:05:58,771 --> 00:06:00,571
Time for someone else to take over.

114
00:06:03,250 --> 00:06:04,211
My survival

115
00:06:05,011 --> 00:06:06,091
must stay secret.

116
00:06:06,891 --> 00:06:07,730
It'd be dangerous

117
00:06:08,170 --> 00:06:09,050
if others know it.

118
00:06:12,691 --> 00:06:13,451
Be careful

119
00:06:14,531 --> 00:06:15,131
then.

120
00:06:16,091 --> 00:06:16,571
I know.

121
00:06:17,410 --> 00:06:17,930
For you,

122
00:06:18,331 --> 00:06:19,410
I'll survive.

123
00:06:23,531 --> 00:06:24,250
(Perfect timing)

124
00:06:24,730 --> 00:06:26,250
(to uncover Grand Tutor's motives,)

125
00:06:27,571 --> 00:06:29,131
(find out where Xue Youshou is,)

126
00:06:30,211 --> 00:06:31,571
(and why he impersonates me.)

127
00:06:45,850 --> 00:06:47,490
(Memorial)
Miss Feng has arrived.

128
00:07:15,571 --> 00:07:16,451
I confirmed

129
00:07:16,971 --> 00:07:17,930
the former Crown Prince

130
00:07:17,930 --> 00:07:19,930
is the illegitimate son
in the south of Xue family,

131
00:07:19,930 --> 00:07:20,610
Xue Youshou.

132
00:07:21,610 --> 00:07:22,691
I've executed him.

133
00:07:45,610 --> 00:07:46,410
Jia Xun.

134
00:07:46,850 --> 00:07:47,771
This nation

135
00:07:49,050 --> 00:07:50,850
belongs to me.

136
00:08:17,691 --> 00:08:18,971
Heavenly blessings descend!

137
00:08:19,771 --> 00:08:21,410
Your Majesty, you're the true emperor.

138
00:08:21,810 --> 00:08:22,891
Your boundless fortune

139
00:08:23,810 --> 00:08:25,891
shall ensure Hua Dynasty's
everlasting prosperity.

140
00:08:26,971 --> 00:08:30,011
Long live His Majesty!

141
00:08:31,331 --> 00:08:33,331
(This Immortal knows
how to pick his moment.)

142
00:08:36,931 --> 00:08:37,530
Rise.

143
00:08:50,890 --> 00:08:51,811
Feng Zuoren.

144
00:08:52,250 --> 00:08:54,130
You seem to have forgotten something.

145
00:08:56,051 --> 00:08:56,650
Your Majesty.

146
00:08:57,411 --> 00:08:58,211
People of Xue family

147
00:08:59,130 --> 00:09:00,530
were also pawns.

148
00:09:01,171 --> 00:09:02,451
It was all that rebel's scheme.

149
00:09:02,850 --> 00:09:03,850
It seems

150
00:09:04,250 --> 00:09:06,331
you want to protect the Xue family.

151
00:09:08,370 --> 00:09:09,091
I wouldn't dare.

152
00:09:09,691 --> 00:09:11,331
I haven't fully verified

153
00:09:11,331 --> 00:09:12,730
Xue Youshou's true identity.

154
00:09:12,971 --> 00:09:13,250
So...

155
00:09:13,250 --> 00:09:14,650
You failed to complete my mission.

156
00:09:15,051 --> 00:09:16,411
Guards! Take her away and

157
00:09:16,691 --> 00:09:17,211
execute her!

158
00:09:35,490 --> 00:09:36,010
Your Majesty.

159
00:09:36,770 --> 00:09:38,931
Avoid bloodshed
within the palace recently.

160
00:09:39,811 --> 00:09:40,331
Wait!

161
00:09:48,610 --> 00:09:49,211
Mr. Immortal,

162
00:09:49,691 --> 00:09:50,890
you make sense.

163
00:09:52,890 --> 00:09:54,650
Thank you for your mercy.

164
00:09:55,650 --> 00:09:56,232
Your Majesty,

165
00:09:57,130 --> 00:10:00,171
I'll obtain a blessed talisman
from the temple

166
00:10:00,730 --> 00:10:03,091
to ward off evil for you.

167
00:10:04,171 --> 00:10:05,370
Thank you, Mr. Immortal.

168
00:10:07,250 --> 00:10:08,091
(Feng Shui array?)

169
00:10:09,010 --> 00:10:11,370
(This man knows Daoist arts well.)

170
00:10:11,931 --> 00:10:13,730
Your worries have eased.

171
00:10:14,130 --> 00:10:15,211
Let me divine.

172
00:10:15,490 --> 00:10:16,610
(Western-style?)

173
00:10:17,370 --> 00:10:19,571
(Blending Eastern and Western styles?)

174
00:10:20,010 --> 00:10:20,691
Your Majesty,

175
00:10:21,650 --> 00:10:23,730
wear red garments

176
00:10:24,211 --> 00:10:25,370
or crimson cords recently.

177
00:10:25,770 --> 00:10:26,770
On an auspicious date,

178
00:10:27,490 --> 00:10:28,730
go visit temples for worship

179
00:10:29,211 --> 00:10:30,890
and pray for protection.

180
00:10:31,171 --> 00:10:31,971
(Indian?)

181
00:10:32,811 --> 00:10:33,490
(Japanese?)

182
00:10:34,411 --> 00:10:35,250
(Why various styles?)

183
00:10:35,850 --> 00:10:36,520
Your Majesty,

184
00:10:37,370 --> 00:10:38,530
the time has come.

185
00:10:38,650 --> 00:10:39,130
Right.

186
00:10:39,931 --> 00:10:40,691
Attendants!

187
00:10:51,370 --> 00:10:51,890
Your Majesty,

188
00:10:52,530 --> 00:10:54,211
this is the Foot Bathing Cauldron,

189
00:10:54,931 --> 00:10:55,971
mandated by heaven,

190
00:10:56,770 --> 00:10:59,130
a divine artifact
protecting all living beings.

191
00:10:59,770 --> 00:11:00,411
Its interior

192
00:11:01,091 --> 00:11:03,091
contains mysterious energies.

193
00:11:03,931 --> 00:11:05,730
Soak nightly for one hour

194
00:11:06,331 --> 00:11:07,890
to strengthen your body

195
00:11:08,411 --> 00:11:11,051
and absorb cosmic essence.

196
00:11:13,890 --> 00:11:15,850
(This is just a regular foot basin.)

197
00:11:16,411 --> 00:11:17,691
(Ten wen for three.)

198
00:11:18,091 --> 00:11:19,370
Heavenly Nectar Oil!

199
00:11:22,451 --> 00:11:24,610
It's extracted from heavenly dew.

200
00:11:25,730 --> 00:11:27,370
When added,

201
00:11:27,730 --> 00:11:30,730
it improves circulation
and nourishes skin.

202
00:11:31,490 --> 00:11:32,811
(Ordinary rose oil,)

203
00:11:33,411 --> 00:11:34,370
(three wen per jug.)

204
00:11:34,530 --> 00:11:35,610
(Enough for half a year.)

205
00:11:36,211 --> 00:11:38,571
This is the Nine-Cycle Golden Pill!

206
00:11:39,730 --> 00:11:41,010
(Is it just brown sugar ball?)

207
00:11:45,370 --> 00:11:46,370
Not yet.

208
00:11:46,890 --> 00:11:48,051
One final step required.

209
00:11:53,730 --> 00:11:54,211
Now!

210
00:12:01,211 --> 00:12:03,171
Mr. Immortal is really remarkable.

211
00:12:03,530 --> 00:12:05,171
Not only medicine and divination,

212
00:12:05,530 --> 00:12:07,250
but also masterful in Feng Shui.

213
00:12:07,610 --> 00:12:09,650
Thanks to him,

214
00:12:10,010 --> 00:12:12,051
Your Majesty's health
has improved greatly.

215
00:12:14,530 --> 00:12:15,411
Is that true?

216
00:12:15,530 --> 00:12:16,370
Absolutely!

217
00:12:17,171 --> 00:12:17,864
Your Majesty,

218
00:12:18,171 --> 00:12:20,250
just follow my methods,

219
00:12:21,051 --> 00:12:21,890
then you

220
00:12:22,291 --> 00:12:23,691
could rule over Hua

221
00:12:24,091 --> 00:12:26,211
for thousands of years.

222
00:12:30,650 --> 00:12:32,411
For thousands of years?

223
00:12:34,730 --> 00:12:35,850
Can my body

224
00:12:37,291 --> 00:12:38,770
truly last that long?

225
00:12:38,931 --> 00:12:39,451
Absolutely.

226
00:12:40,530 --> 00:12:42,171
Based on your birth chart

227
00:12:43,250 --> 00:12:45,370
and current celestial observations,

228
00:12:46,770 --> 00:12:48,650
if you want to stay healthy,

229
00:12:50,130 --> 00:12:52,291
avoid bloodshed recently.

230
00:12:52,530 --> 00:12:55,171
Otherwise, it'll diminish your fortune.

231
00:12:56,451 --> 00:12:57,211
In that case,

232
00:12:58,250 --> 00:12:58,811
I shall

233
00:12:59,770 --> 00:13:01,490
temporarily spare Feng Zuoren

234
00:13:02,130 --> 00:13:03,411
and the entire Xue family.

235
00:13:06,730 --> 00:13:07,250
Your Majesty,

236
00:13:08,091 --> 00:13:09,691
time to go to sleep.

237
00:13:10,130 --> 00:13:13,331
Align your head 45 degrees southwest,

238
00:13:13,691 --> 00:13:16,130
using the Heavenly Pillow I provided,

239
00:13:16,770 --> 00:13:20,291
to optimally absorb the moon's essence,

240
00:13:20,691 --> 00:13:22,130
purify the toxins in your body,

241
00:13:22,291 --> 00:13:23,530
and get restful sleep.

242
00:13:26,331 --> 00:13:27,411
Thank you, Mr. Immortal.

243
00:13:38,331 --> 00:13:38,811
