270
00:14:43,010 --> 00:14:44,411
Thank you for saving my life.

271
00:14:45,211 --> 00:14:47,530
Your mighty powers earn imperial favor.

272
00:14:48,010 --> 00:14:49,931
Might I request a divination?

273
00:14:55,850 --> 00:14:57,291
